@NODE Introduction
@TITLE "Miliarderzy  Introduction"


    @{b}Introduction@{ub}

    Miliarderzy is multiplatforms (morphos,linux,windows) quiz game which is
    made by members of Harvester demoscene group. The game is mix of
    some tv-shows and our ideas. Now we give you only demo version of this
    freeware game. We still searching for people who want to help us with
    other launguages. For more question, sugestion, opinions write to :
    stefkos@poczta.fm or cadavar@interia.pl. We hope that you'll enjoy this
    game!


P.S. Sorry for our English :)
    

@ENDNODE

@NODE Requirements
@TITLE "Miliarderzy  Requirements"


    @{b}Requirements@{ub}


    - MorphOS version:
      - powerSDL library 10.0 version or higher
        (thx goto itix and   http://sdl.noidea.hu/  crew )

    - Windows version:
      - sdl.dll
      - sdl_image.dll
      - sdl_mixer.dll
      - sdl_ttf.dll
      - png.dll
      - jpeg.dll
      - zlib.dll
      - msvcrtd.dll

    - Linux version:
      - need's SDL libraries installed in latest version



@ENDNODE

@NODE Installation
@TITLE "Miliarderzy  Installation"


    @{b}Installation@{ub}


    Copy this game into folder where you have games.

@ENDNODE

@NODE demo
@TITLE "Miliarderzy  Demo version"


    @{b}Start@{ub}

    Launch game , select your language , select start option,
    enter your name and then you can play.

